  "technical_rules_for_ai": {
    "build_stack": [
      "HTML",
      "CSS",
      "minimal JavaScript"
    ],
    "requirements": [
      "Código limpio y semántico",
      "No usar librerías pesadas salvo necesidad real",
      "Dejar arquitectura lista para escalar a e-commerce",
      "Centralizar tokens visuales",
      "No inventar colores ni tipografías fuera del sistema",
      "No usar Gopher en minúscula",
      "Usar Articulat CF en cuerpo y UI",
      "Preparar placeholders editables para menú, eventos y tienda"
    ],
    "file_output_expected": [
      "index.html",
      "css/style.css",
      "js/script.js",
      "assets/images/",
      "assets/logo/"
    ]
  },
  "master_prompt_for_codex": "Read and follow as source of truth:\n- the Lombardo brandbook PDF\n- brand-guidelines.md\n- design-system.md\n- website-structure.md\n- content-copy.md\n- ai-instructions.md\n- project-context.md\n- lombardo-ai-design-system.json\n\nBuild or redesign the Lombardo website accordingly.\n\nHard rules:\n- Use only the official color palette from lombardo-ai-design-system.json.\n- Use Gopher only in uppercase for headings, short statements and display text.\n- Use Articulat CF for paragraphs, UI, menu content and long text.\n- Keep the website aligned with Lombardo's identity: community, warmth, differentiation, tradition + modernity.\n- The website must include Home, Nosotros, Carta, Café, Vinos, Experiencias, Eventos, Club Lombardo, Tienda, Galería and Contacto.\n- Include digital menu, location with embedded map, WhatsApp CTA, Instagram link and a future-ready ecommerce section.\n- Preserve a premium but accessible aesthetic.\n- Make the site fully responsive and semantically structured.\n- Favor clarity, atmosphere and brand consistency over visual noise.\n\nRequired homepage order:\nHero → Concepto → Nosotros breve → Carta destacada → Café → Vinos → Experiencias → Eventos → Club Lombardo → Galería → Ubicación con mapa → Contacto → Footer\n\nOutput:\n- index.html\n- css/style.css\n- js/script.js\n- any necessary supporting folders and assets references\n"
}